Class AudioDAO

java.lang.Object
it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.dao.playable.AudioDAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAudioDAO
public class AudioDAO extends Object implements IAudioDAO
Implementation of the methods declared in IAudioDAO. It encapsulates database interactions, providing a clean and reusable interface for accessing JBAudio data.
